    "_description": "Agent execution defaults. recursion_limit and compaction.ratio are sourced from the environment (AGENT_RECURSION_LIMIT, COMPACTION_RATIO via core.config.Settings) — these JSON values are last-resort fallbacks when the env vars aren't loaded (e.g. one-off CLI scripts that bypass Settings). default_temperature stays JSON-resident since it has no env override yet.",
